<p>Lens is available as a <a href="https://packagist.org/packages/lens/lens">Composer package</a>.
This is a good way to get regular updates.</p>

<div class="terminal">
	<div>Add the Composer package to your project:</div>
	<pre><code>composer require lens/lens</code></pre>
</div>

<p>And now you can use Lens:</p>

<div class="terminal">
	<div>View the version information:</div>
	<pre><code>./vendor/bin/lens --version</code></pre>
</div>
